-to985bbon.jpg', NULL, 'na', NULL, '2025-10-21 18:09:25', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '2025-10-23 09:51:17', 'brb99446033cea4a1bb3ed01507e611ced', 'agffa70e8079be4ce298d88a7b8934c1d4', 'agent'),
('cp5dd4a4bae24b4ab8b1cea5c39969afb7', NULL, 'Title', '<h>🎯 Campaign Mission</h>\n\n<p>Transform your brand story into authentic, engaging content that resonates with your audience and drives real results.</p>\n\n<h>📋 What We\'re Looking For</h>\n\n<li><strong>Genuine, authentic content</strong> showcasing our brand naturally</li>\n<li><strong>High-quality visuals</strong> that align with our aesthetic and values</li>\n<li><strong>Compelling captions</strong> that spark conversation and engagement</li>\n<li><strong>Strategic hashtag usage</strong> to maximize reach and discoverability</li>\n\n<h>✨ Content Requirements</h>\n\n<li>Include provided brand mentions and hashtags</li>\n<li>Feature clear, action-driven call-to-actions</li>\n<li>Post during peak engagement hours for your audience</li>\n<li>Tag our official social media accounts</li>\n<li>Maintain brand voice while adding your personal touch</li>\n\n<h>💡 Creative Freedom</h>\n\n<p>We believe your unique perspective is what makes this collaboration special. Feel free to interpret our brand through your lens while staying true to our core message and values.</p>\n\n<h>🎁 Collaboration Benefits</h>\n\n<p>[Specify products, services, compensation, or exclusive perks]</p>\n\n<h>📅 Campaign Timeline</h>\n\n<li><strong>Content creation deadline:</strong> [Date]</li>\n<li><strong>Publishing schedule:</strong> [Date range]</li>\n<li><strong>Campaign duration:</strong> [Start date] to [End date]</li>\n\n<h>💬 Questions & Support</h>\n\n<p>We\'re here to support your creative process! Reach out anytime for clarification, additional resources, or brainstorming sessions.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Ready to create something amazing together? Let\'s make magic happen! ✨🚀</strong></p>', 'Lead Generation & List Growth', '2025-10-30', 0.00, 'b88cf0fb5eee6405a8c166f4bde6eb810', 'open_to_applications', '2025-10-14', 20.00, 0.00, 'https://sg-cdn.tekjuice.xyz/gems/1759870294614-7mxa51yw5.jpg', NULL, 'na', NULL, '2025-10-07 20:51:35', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '2025-10-07 21:05:10', 'b88cf0fb5eee6405a8c166f4bde6eb810', 'b88cf0fb5eee6405a8c166f4bde6eb810', 'brand'),
('cp66262e5df23845deadab6d6097aedd3c', '677b9be5-0264-4e37-bc9f-502cf7ce5eab', 'Gems in action ', 'Gems in Action is a controlled pre-launch campaign designed to help us understand what works best when connecting influencers and brands on the Social Gems platform. Before we officially roll out our UK-wide launch, we’re running this targeted initiative to gather real-world data, refine our processes, and ensure our approach delivers maximum results for both creators and brands.\n\nThe campaign will focus on three priority sectors, giving us the opportunity to work closely with a carefully selected group of influencers and brands in each category. Influencers will be encouraged to create authentic, engaging content that not only showcases the brand’s products or services but also reflects their own unique voice and style. By doing this, we aim to demonstrate the power of genuine, trust-based connections between creators and audiences.\n\nWe will test different types of collaborations — from product showcases to lifestyle storytelling — and explore a variety of creative formats, including short-form videos, reels, and high-impact static posts. Each collaboration will be tracked using measurable metrics such as reach, engagement, and sign-up conversions to the Social Gems platform.\n\nAn important aspect of Gems in Action is feedback. Both creators and brands will be encouraged to share their insights, experiences, and suggestions throughout the campaign. This will give us valuable qualitative data to complement the quantitative metrics, allowing us to identify which campaign styles resonate most, which types of influencers drive the highest ROI, and what messaging sparks the most audience engagement.\n\nOur goal is to use this test phase to build a playbook for our full UK launch — a blueprint based on real performance, not assumptions. Once the campaign wraps, we’ll analyse the results, optimise our recruitment strategy, and fine-tune our content approach so that when Social Gems goes live UK-wide, we’re ready to deliver a proven, impactful experience for every creator', 'Lead Generation & List Growth', '2025-08-31', 0.00, 'b92d5dc5bb14b493eb6a534f311669d23', 'open_to_applications', '2025-08-25', 250.00, 0.00, 'https://social-gems.s3.amazonaws.com/gems/1755874859473-1p9cwiy5l.tmp-1-1755874859059', NULL, 'na', NULL, '2025-08-22 15:00:59', NULL, NULL, 2, NULL, '2025-08-22 16:08:44', 'b92d5dc5bb14b493eb6a534f311669d23', 'b92d5dc5bb14b493eb6a534f311669d23', 'brand'),
