('cpa222c2e665394f6dbf7f432da31e7f8a', NULL, 'Pastry Party', 'Freshly baked pastries fill the air with a sweet, buttery aroma — golden croissants, soft cinnamon rolls, and flaky danishes layered with rich cream and fruit. Each bite melts perfectly, offering warmth, comfort, and indulgence. From morning treats to evening desserts, pastries turn every moment into something special and delicious.', 'Increase Brand Awareness', '2025-11-24', 0.00, 'bfc40f8f0f16146cbb965bbec69df434a', 'draft', '2025-10-24', 0.00, 0.00, 'https://sg-cdn.tekjuice.xyz/gems/1761229631415-1gd25q91t.jpg', NULL, 'na', NULL, '2025-10-23 14:27:12', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'bfc40f8f0f16146cbb965bbec69df434a', 'ag6d5a1dc789f24bd0ba26b05fcac40e27', 'agent'),
('cpa378dad0b34a4289bec9bde040ad20d5', NULL, 'GLOW FOR LESS', 'The campaign objective is to get people to know about the current offer on Maybelline lipglosses, which are now going for KSH 1250 on verified websites and approved in-stores like SuperCosmetics<br><br>Creators are supposed to do talking videos featuring/ showing the lipgloss and highlighting main ingredients that are in the lipgloss.<br><br>Creators MUST use the campaign hashtags and videos MUST be approved before posting.&nbsp;', 'Increase Brand Awareness', '2025-11-28', 0.00, 'bc68a409792b141ca9c3ffabfa546b491', 'draft', '2025-10-28', 0.00, 0.00, 'https://sg-cdn.tekjuice.xyz/gems/1761558383738-x4njfyfvl.png', NULL, 'na', NULL, '2025-10-27 09:46:24', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'bc68a409792b141ca9c3ffabfa546b491', 'ag0c04e913b47b4261beec948fd9b03565', 'agent'),
