('cpaeae92d9c5bb448c94cfae897ac7d199', NULL, 'Ariel', 'Ariel’s “Power in Every Wash” campaign celebrates the confidence that comes with spotless clothes and a fresh start every day. Built around the idea that cleanliness empowers, the campaign highlights Ariel’s advanced stain-removal technology that tackles even the toughest stains — from mud to curry, oil to ink — leaving clothes brilliantly clean and vibrant.\n\nThrough real-life stories, engaging visuals, and influencer collaborations, the campaign connects with modern families and individuals who never compromise on excellence. It emphasizes that Ariel is more than just a detergent — it’s a partner in helping people look and feel their best, no matter what life throws at them.\n\nWith a focus on innovation, freshness, and trust, the campaign inspires consumers to “let your confidence shine,” knowing that Ariel’s superior cleaning power has their back.', 'Drive Website Traffic', '2025-10-21', 0.00, 'bcb2f9aa1862346ceb175f1cf0bd468eb', 'draft', '2025-10-18', 20.00, 0.00, 'https://sg-cdn.tekjuice.xyz/gems/1760429035436-b83td0fx1.webp', NULL, 'na', NULL, '2025-10-14 08:03:56', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, 'bcb2f9aa1862346ceb175f1cf0bd468eb', '89899898998', 'agent'),
('cpb29f8eb1c7b24419b39dc6cb7137d52e', NULL, 'Clean Beyond the Surface', 'The “Clean Beyond the Surface” campaign celebrates the power of a detergent that does more than just wash clothes — it restores freshness, comfort, and confidence to every moment of your day. Designed for today’s busy lifestyles, this campaign showcases how our detergent goes deep into fabric fibers to remove dirt, sweat, and stubborn stains while leaving a long-lasting fresh scent that keeps you feeling clean all day.\n\nThrough vibrant storytelling and relatable visuals, the campaign captures families, professionals, and everyday heroes who trust our detergent to keep their clothes spotless and soft. It emphasizes that cleanliness isn’t just about appearance — it’s about feeling good, confident, and ready to take on the world.\n\nWith a focus on deep cleaning technology, freshness, and care, the campaign reinforces our promise: every wash brings not just clean clothes, but a clean start.', 'Boost Sales Conversion', '2025-10-22', 0.00, 'b1cc8b76ecd564cae93266ffd3e6d3745', 'draft', '2025-10-18', 30.00, 0.00, 'https://sg-cdn.tekjuice.xyz/gems/1760430101196-rccgcblnp.webp', NULL, 'na', NULL, '2025-10-14 08:21:41', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, 'b1cc8b76ecd564cae93266ffd3e6d3745', '89899898998', 'agent'),
('cpb74b23d8a0344fce9e0c2e474d605ce0', NULL, 'Title 15', '<h>🎯 Campaign Mission</h>\n\n<p>Transform your brand story into authentic, engaging content that resonates with your audience and drives real results.</p>\n\n<h>📋 What We\'re Looking For</h>\n\n<li><strong>Genuine, authentic content</strong> showcasing our brand naturally</li>\n<li><strong>High-quality visuals</strong> that align with our aesthetic and values</li>\n<li><strong>Compelling captions</strong> that spark conversation and engagement</li>\n<li><strong>Strategic hashtag usage</strong> to maximize reach and discoverability</li>\n\n<h>✨ Content Requirements</h>\n\n<li>Include provided brand mentions and hashtags</li>\n<li>Feature clear, action-driven call-to-actions</li>\n<li>Post during peak engagement hours for your audience</li>\n<li>Tag our official social media accounts</li>\n<li>Maintain brand voice while adding your personal touch</li>\n\n<h>💡 Creative Freedom</h>\n\n<p>We believe your unique perspective is what makes this collaboration special. Feel free to interpret our brand through your lens while staying true to our core message and values.</p>\n\n<h>🎁 Collaboration Benefits</h>\n\n<p>[Specify products, services, compensation, or exclusive perks]</p>\n\n<h>📅 Campaign Timeline</h>\n\n<li><strong>Content creation deadline:</strong> [Date]</li>\n<li><strong>Publishing schedule:</strong> [Date range]</li>\n<li><strong>Campaign duration:</strong> [Start date] to [End date]</li>\n\n<h>💬 Questions & Support</h>\n\n<p>We\'re here to support your creative process! Reach out anytime for clarification, additional resources, or brainstorming sessions.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Ready to create something amazing together? Let\'s make magic happen! ✨🚀</strong></p>', 'SEO & Organic Visibility', '2025-10-31', 0.00, 'b88cf0fb5eee6405a8c166f4bde6eb810', 'open_to_applications', '2025-10-13', 16.00, 0.00, 'https://sg-cdn.tekjuice.xyz/gems/1759992983127-f40tjht6r.jpg', NULL, 'na', NULL, '2025-10-09 06:56:24', NULL, NULL