('grp_82c7f81618f74d30a91ce5f8555d83c8', 'Light in the Night: A Journey of Faith', 'Spend a night dedicated to deepening your testimony, strengthening bonds, and drawing closer to Christ. Light in the Night is an overnight gathering for youth and families within the Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints, filled with uplifting devotionals, group discussions, scripture study, and spiritual music. Together, we’ll explore how to stand as disciples of Christ in a world full of challenges, and how His light can guide us through every season of life. Expect moments of quiet reflection, joyful fellowship, and activities that inspire both heart and mind.', 'Post relevant information', 'open', '', '', 'active', '2025-08-21 19:03:27', 'grp_82c7f81618f74d30a91ce5f8555d83c8', 'yes', 'b4c1231d885f54a78824fe698a53c1872', NULL, NULL, '2025-08-21 19:03:27'),
